text:
Iowa State aims for second Big 12 winIowa State aims for second Big 12 win Published 2:15 PM CDT Oct 10, 2015 A Large Text Photos 
The Iowa State Cyclones are on the road to go head-to-head against Texas Tech. The Cyclones head to Lubbock off a triumphant 38-13 win in their Big 12 opener against Kansas. Other Stories 
Kickoff is scheduled for 2:30 p.m., and the game will air on FSN.
